MrsSiew
Singapore, Singapore450 contributions
Beautiful and scenic
Beautiful scenic views. Cold and windy in December. Our family went for a day trip . (USD60 P/P booked with hotel we were staying). Picked up time from hotel at 8am returned to hotel around 830pm. From Hoam Kiem area to Ha Long by coach was about 2 hrs 30 mins. Cruise with buffet was about 1 hrs 30 mins at the Ha long Bay and 1st stop was Surprising Cave followed by 15 or 20 mins speed boat (paid 240K dong each separately not included) and bamboo boat came with the day trip package. Next was the Ti Top cave and back to port.
Overall a very nice experience and had achieved one of my bucket list.
