Pristine Heavenly Paradise
Dec 2023 â€¢ Couples
Ha Long Bay offers pristine locations for weekend gate way.
The water is clam, emerald Green offering perfect conditions for kayaking and boating. Other than the unique landscape of limestone islands poping out of sea, it offers explorations to caves and small prinstine in crowded beach as well. Smaller the tour grouo better is the exploration opportunity at caves.
How ever, the Bay is too crowded with numbers of cruises being operating In the bay and additional day cruises.
Night offers great opportunity for squid fishing.
